<item>
            <title>[HBASE-12701] Document how to set the split policy on a given table</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12701</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Need to document in the ref guide how to set/change the region split policy for a single table user the API and the HBase shell as noted below as an example.&lt;br/&gt;
Using Java:&lt;br/&gt;
HTableDescriptor tableDesc = new HTableDescriptor(&quot;test&quot;);&lt;br/&gt;
tableDesc.setValue(HTableDescriptor.SPLIT_POLICY, ConstantSizeRegionSplitPolicy.class.getName());&lt;br/&gt;
tableDesc.addFamily(new HColumnDescriptor(Bytes.toBytes(&quot;cf1&quot;)));&lt;br/&gt;
admin.createTable(tableDesc);&lt;br/&gt;
Using HBase Shell:&lt;br/&gt;
create &apos;test&apos;, {METHOD =&amp;gt; &apos;table_att&apos;, CONFIG =&amp;gt; {&apos;SPLIT_POLICY&apos; =&amp;gt; &apos;org.apache.hadoop.hbase.regionserver.ConstantSizeRegionSplitPolicy&apos;}},&lt;/p&gt;
{NAME =&amp;gt; &apos;cf1&apos;}</description>
